---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="The Institutional Church — The Priesthood — Nazaryah"
  description="False prophets, megachurch empires, and the New Apostolic Reformation. The function of the institutional church is identical to every pagan priesthood before it — standing between the people and the Creator."
>
  <div class="sw-wrap">

    <!-- ── HERO ── -->
    <section class="sw-hero">
      <p class="sw-label">&#8213; The Priesthood &#8213;</p>
      <h1 class="sw-title">The Institutional Church</h1>
      <p class="sw-sub">
        False Prophets, Mega-Temples, and the New Apostolic Reformation
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- ── INTRO ── -->
    <section class="sw-section">
      <div class="sw-prose">
        <p>
          The second branch of the modern priesthood does not wear lab coats. It wears vestments, business suits, and designer sneakers. It operates from stages, not laboratories. It uses worship music, not equations. But the function is identical to every priesthood that has ever existed: it stands between the people and the Creator, claims authority to interpret truth, and punishes those who dissent — not with peer review, but with excommunication, social exile, and spiritual intimidation.
        </p>
        <p>
          This page examines three layers of the institutional church system: the historical absorption of sun worship into the Roman church, the modern false prophet movement, and the New Apostolic Reformation — the most organized and dangerous expression of the institutional priesthood alive today.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ── SIX STUDIES ── -->
    <section class="sw-accordion-section">
      <p class="sw-accordion-label">&#8213; Six Studies &#8213;</p>
      <h2 class="sw-accordion-title">The Foundation, The Wolves, and The Network</h2>
      <div class="sw-mini-grid">

        <a href="/sun-worship/the-priesthood/roman-church" class="sw-mini-card sw-mini-card-live">
          <span class="sw-mini-title">Roman Church</span>
          <span class="sw-mini-poetic">From Mithras to Mass</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/sun-worship/the-priesthood/false-prophets" class="sw-mini-card sw-mini-card-live">
          <span class="sw-mini-title">False Prophets</span>
          <span class="sw-mini-poetic">Wolves in Sheep's Clothing</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/sun-worship/the-priesthood/nar" class="sw-mini-card sw-mini-card-live">
          <span class="sw-mini-title">NAR</span>
          <span class="sw-mini-poetic">The New Apostolic Reformation</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/sun-worship/the-priesthood/political-christianity" class="sw-mini-card sw-mini-card-live">
          <span class="sw-mini-title">Political Christianity</span>
          <span class="sw-mini-poetic">When the Church Weds the State</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/sun-worship/the-priesthood/megachurches" class="sw-mini-card sw-mini-card-live">
          <span class="sw-mini-title">Megachurches</span>
          <span class="sw-mini-poetic">The Laodicean Stage</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/sun-worship/the-priesthood/protestantism" class="sw-mini-card sw-mini-card-live">
          <span class="sw-mini-title">Protestantism</span>
          <span class="sw-mini-poetic">The Half-Finished Reformation</span>
        </a>

      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ── QUOTE ── -->
    <section class="sw-footer-quote">
      <p class="sw-quote-text">"Beware of false prophets, which come to you in sheep's clothing, but inwardly they are ravening wolves."</p>
      <p class="sw-quote-ref">— Matthew 7:15</p>
    </section>

  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .sw-wrap {
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #0e0904 0%, #1a1208 20%, #160f07 100%);
    color: #f0e0bf;
    font-family: 'Crimson Pro', 'Crimson Text', Georgia, serif;
    min-height: 80vh;
  }

  .sw-hero {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 5rem 1.5rem 3.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #4a3218;
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 0%, rgba(180, 100, 20, 0.2), transparent 70%),
      linear-gradient(180deg, #0a0602 0%, #1a1208 100%);
  }

  .sw-label {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 4px;
    color: #8a6028;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .sw-title {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #f0e0bf;
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }

  .sw-sub {
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 2vw, 1.2rem);
    color: #c4a46b;
    font-style: italic;
    max-width: 580px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .sw-section {
    padding: 3.5rem 1.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #2e1f0d;
  }

  .sw-prose {
    max-width: 680px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    line-height: 1.85;
    color: #d9c9a8;
  }

  .sw-prose p { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .sw-prose p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

  .sw-scripture-block {
    padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
    border-left: 3px solid #BA7517;
    background: rgba(10, 6, 2, 0.4);
    border-radius: 0 4px 4px 0;
  }

  .sw-scripture-label {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
    font-size: 9px;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #BA7517;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem !important;
  }

  /* ── ACCORDION ── */
  .sw-accordion-section {
    padding: 4rem 1.5rem 5rem;
    text-align: center;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #2e1f0d;
  }

  .sw-accordion-label {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 4px;
    color: #6a4820;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .sw-accordion-title {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
    font-size: clamp(1.4rem, 3vw, 2rem);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #f0e0bf;
    margin: 0 0 2.5rem;
  }

  .sw-accordion-sub {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: #8a6a38;
    font-style: italic;
    margin: 0 auto 2.5rem;
    max-width: 500px;
  }

  .sw-accordion {
    max-width: 820px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .sw-detail { border-bottom: 1px solid #2a1a08; }
  .sw-detail:first-child { border-top: 1px solid #2a1a08; }

  .sw-summary {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: 1.25rem 0.5rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    list-style: none;
    transition: background 0.15s;
  }

  .sw-summary::-webkit-details-marker { display: none; }
  .sw-summary:hover { background: rgba(186, 117, 23, 0.04); }

  .sw-head {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.2rem;
    flex: 1;
  }

  .sw-head-clear {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 2vw, 1.2rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 2.5px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #f0e0bf;
    line-height: 1.15;
  }

  .sw-head-poetic {
    font-family: 'Crimson Pro', 'Crimson Text', Georgia, serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: #c4a46b;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .sw-part-label {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
    font-size: 9px;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #BA7517;
    font-weight: 700;
    white-space: nowrap;
    min-width: 80px;
  }

  .sw-part-title {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
    font-size: clamp(0.85rem, 1.5vw, 1rem);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #f0e0bf;
    flex: 1;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  }

  .sw-chevron {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: #5a3a10;
    transition: transform 0.2s;
    margin-left: auto;
  }

  .sw-detail[open] .sw-chevron { transform: rotate(45deg); }

  .sw-body {
    padding: 0 0.5rem 2rem;
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.85;
    color: #d9c9a8;
    border-top: 1px solid #1e1208;
  }

  .sw-body p { margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .sw-body p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
  .sw-body strong { color: #e0c88a; }

  .sw-body-heading {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 1.5px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #8B3A0A;
    margin: 1.75rem 0 0.75rem;
  }

  .sw-body-heading:first-child { margin-top: 1.5rem; }

  /* ── COMING SOON ── */
  .sw-coming-section {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 4rem 1.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #2e1f0d;
    background: rgba(8, 5, 2, 0.4);
  }

  .sw-coming-label {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 4px;
    color: #4a3018;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .sw-coming-title {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
    font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 2.5vw, 1.5rem);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #6a5030;
    margin: 0 0 2rem;
  }

  .sw-mini-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
    gap: 1rem;
    max-width: 820px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .sw-mini-card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
    text-decoration: none;
    padding: 1rem 1rem 1.1rem;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #2a1a08 0%, #1e1208 100%);
    border: 1px solid #3a2410;
    border-radius: 12px;
    cursor: default;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
  }

  .sw-mini-card-soon {
    cursor: default;
  }

  .sw-mini-card-live {
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #9a4a1a 0%, #7a3a10 55%, #4e2208 100%);
    border-color: rgba(186, 117, 23, 0.4);
    cursor: pointer;
    box-shadow:
      0 4px 14px rgba(186, 117, 23, 0.18),
      inset 0 2px 4px rgba(220, 160, 80, 0.25),
      inset 0 -2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
  }

  .sw-mini-card-live:hover {
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #b05a28 0%, #9a4a1a 55%, #6e3210 100%);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow:
      0 8px 20px rgba(186, 117, 23, 0.3),
      inset 0 2px 4px rgba(220, 170, 100, 0.3),
      inset 0 -2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
  }

  .sw-mini-title {
    display: block;
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #9a7840;
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .sw-mini-card-live .sw-mini-title {
    color: #fff5e0;
  }

  .sw-mini-poetic {
    display: block;
    font-family: 'Crimson Pro', 'Crimson Text', Georgia, serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: #6a5030;
    line-height: 1.35;
  }

  .sw-mini-card-live .sw-mini-poetic {
    color: #f0d8a4;
  }

  /* ── FOOTER ── */
  .sw-footer-quote {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #160f07 0%, #0e0904 100%);
  }

  .sw-quote-text {
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 2vw, 1.2rem);
    font-style: italic;
    color: #c4a46b;
    max-width: 620px;
    margin: 0 auto 0.5rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  .sw-quote-ref {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
    font-size: 9px;
    letter-spacing: 1.5px;
    color: #5a3e1a;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
</style>
